{"tid":1212281,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 談Water Fire Extinguisher之原理","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T19:32:37.000Z","uid":67995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a42b42e5093b0ed9c461b3c67376687691739d85","tid":1212281,"uid":67995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9WO6mT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9WO6mT.png&h=054ad05c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到餐廳啲人話佢叫水劑<br />\n所以就好奇上網搵吓<br />\n原來大致原理係有枝氮氣噴氣 高壓噴入面啲水出嚟<br />\n仲有分9L裝同6L裝 好似6L輕啲都夠滅怕水的野啦<br />\n都唔明餐廳要咁大枝做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問吓巴絲們我有冇理解錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢夢見旺角新填地街好多人係度搬呢啲樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0746d87f90971476ca6f2a9d6f9cff670b9f67ee","tid":1212281,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69898bd71c88078953361e1bca6fe0c835f56086","tid":1212281,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:32:37.000Z","msg":"Weapons of opportunity，緊急先好用唔係好快用晒"}]}